# Cloudflare Pages redirects
# Production URL: https://mirrorbite.starving-effort.com/<path>
#
# Cloudflare Pages auto-handles clean URLs (/privacy serves /privacy.html).
# We only need backward-compat redirects for old paths used during development.

# Backward-compat for old /mirrorbite/ paths
/mirrorbite                /  301
/mirrorbite/privacy        /privacy  301
/mirrorbite/terms          /terms    301
/mirrorbite/support        /support  301
/mirrorbite/privacy.html   /privacy  301
/mirrorbite/terms.html     /terms    301
/mirrorbite/support.html   /support  301
